WEBVTT

00:19.234 --> 00:19.795
Well, hello there.

00:21.137 --> 00:22.479
I'm so glad you could be here.

00:25.804 --> 00:32.313
It's Christmas time, the season of Twinkling Lights, hot cocoa that's way too hot at the first sip.

00:35.378 --> 00:39.364
And snow that looks so magical until you have to shovel it.

00:42.188 --> 00:48.978
And let's be honest, Christmas also means wrapping gifts at midnight, forgetting where you hid your presents,

00:51.106 --> 00:55.531
and eating just one more cookie, which somehow turns into three.

00:59.717 --> 01:08.147
But maybe Christmas isn't just about presents, trees, and trying to untangle the same string of lights you swore you threw away last year.

01:09.609 --> 01:10.670
It's about something bigger.

01:12.092 --> 01:20.402
It's about joy that lasts, hope that doesn't fade, and a love that came down to earth wrapped in swaddling clothes.

01:20.770 --> 01:21.271
Jesus.

01:22.073 --> 01:28.185
So right now, let's laugh a little louder, sing a little stronger, and celebrate a little brighter.

01:29.167 --> 01:33.696
Because this is Christmas, and there's no better reason to be joyful than this.

01:35.239 --> 01:40.850
As a matter of fact, a sentiment, put my favorite record on.

03:56.514 --> 03:59.358
I've been waiting to say that since Thanksgiving.

03:59.418 --> 04:00.279
I'm gonna say it again.

04:00.419 --> 04:01.701
Merry Christmas everybody.

04:01.801 --> 04:07.468
It's so good to be with you no matter where you are joining us from, especially if you are new here.

04:07.969 --> 04:10.512
We are so glad that you are here.

04:10.572 --> 04:12.354
And what a fun way to start the service.

04:12.775 --> 04:18.903
I literally grew up on Claymation Rudolph and putting Jingle Bell Rock on mom and dad's record player.

04:19.564 --> 04:24.530
But just like the video says, Christmas is so much bigger, so much deeper than that.

04:24.930 --> 04:32.062
It's about a joy that lasts, a hope that doesn't fade and a love that came from heaven to earth to be with us.

04:32.363 --> 04:33.565
And his name is Jesus.

04:34.146 --> 04:35.348
It's the reason we gather.

04:35.388 --> 04:37.131
It's the reason we are all here.

04:37.231 --> 04:38.714
It's the reason we worship.

04:39.174 --> 04:41.478
And something powerful happens when we do it together.

04:41.579 --> 04:45.906
So come on church, stand to your feet and let's worship together.

17:00.162 --> 17:05.430
We're so thankful for who you are to us.

17:06.171 --> 17:09.476
We're so thankful for the love that you have for each of us.

17:10.658 --> 17:20.874
A love so great that you came down to earth so that we could be close to you, so that we could experience joy and hope in your name, Jesus.

17:22.035 --> 17:29.106
And so I pray today in the busyness of this season, what our eyes, what our hearts be fixed on here, Jesus.

17:29.378 --> 17:31.363
You are so worthy of our praise.

17:31.383 --> 17:33.047
You're so worthy of our worship.

17:33.067 --> 17:35.714
So would you be glorified in this place today?

17:36.416 --> 17:37.298
We love you so much.

17:37.358 --> 17:38.922
We pray this all in your powerful name.

17:38.942 --> 17:40.125
Amen.

17:40.185 --> 17:41.428
Amen, everybody.

17:41.508 --> 17:42.451
So good to be with you.

17:42.471 --> 17:43.794
We can take a seat.

17:48.738 --> 17:54.350
I just love seeing Silent Night and getting to hear everyone's voice in the room, not as such an amazing moment.

17:54.370 --> 18:07.218
Yeah, it's when we do almost every year, and every time we do it, I think about what it would have actually been like to be there when Jesus came to earth, when God entered humanity through a humble baby boy.

18:07.298 --> 18:07.920
It's amazing.

18:07.940 --> 18:08.942
That story is amazing.

18:08.962 --> 18:10.586
It is why we celebrate Christmas.

18:10.626 --> 18:13.093
Yes, that is why we are celebrating for sure.

18:13.734 --> 18:16.922
And you know, these services, there is a lot for our volunteers to do.

18:16.962 --> 18:21.253
And so this next weekend, we actually don't have in-person services.

18:21.915 --> 18:24.882
